MoreMsg              none              none
; Combining behavior of listchar highlight in nvim
; (only in nvim, https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/23869)
; * It should not be combined with :syn highlights.
;   This can be enforced by using nocombine in NonText.
; * The desired behavior for combining with Visual/Search is
;   fg = bg4 and bg = Visual/Search color.
;   For this to work, Visual/Search should not use reverse.
;   But not using reverse in Visual/Search result in
;   weird combining with base groups that use reverse (e.g., Todo).
;   To fix this, use nocombine in Visual/Search.
;   Ideally, I want to preserve other attrs, but that's not possible.
;   Maybe add attrs like "noreverse" in nvim?
NonText              bg4               none              nocombine
Pmenu                none              bgblue
PmenuExtra           none              bgblue
PmenuKind            none              bgblue            bold
